So I asked Lucy very kindly
if she could go and find

00:57:34.330 --> 00:57:35.550
the bits of spacecraft.

00:57:35.550 --> 00:57:36.280
Do you want to--

00:57:36.280 --> 00:57:39.340
very carefully-- we'll
wheel it out the front here.

