No.

01:01:48.940 --> 01:01:54.660
OK, so we'll wheel these off
before I actually touch them.

01:01:54.660 --> 01:01:56.075
They're broken already.

01:01:56.075 --> 01:01:56.700
They're broken.

01:01:56.700 --> 01:01:57.200
That's OK.

01:01:57.200 --> 01:01:59.344
Round of applause for
